.TH PRODBOX_gateway 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-gateway \- Gateway daemon operations
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox gateway
.SH DESCRIPTION
Distributed gateway daemon commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBstart\fR
